726140f-a.title: Queens: Beach 20th Street - Mott Avenue
726140f-a.text:
Beach 20th Street, northward to Mott Ave., showing at the S.W.
corner a turreted building housing the Capital Lunch in 1923.
January 1923.
Eugene L. Armbruster Collection.
